alt=&#34;Screenshot depicting the namecheap domain landing page&#34;/&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The hardest part is deciding on the domain name&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
